{"tid":1653843,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[北區大埔手足入] 跨區開花投票","createTime":"2019-10-14T09:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T04:49:52.000Z","uid":129828,"like":18,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe741e7249801076c614d109b47dbf7330ce555","tid":1653843,"uid":129828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:23:09.000Z","msg":"隨遇而安巴打頭先開咗以下既post<br />\n18區分區太散, 重新組合過, 大家覺得呢個組合點?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1653375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1653375</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見到大部分區都冇乜異議<br />\n係得番北區大埔手足就住出唔出沙田有好大分歧<br />\n<br />\n所以想開個新post 集中討論北區 大埔手足既諗法<br />\n<br />\n但係由於北區戰力單薄 所以投票選項係唔包括北區獨立開花<br />\n<br />\n投票<br />\n如果手足想 北區+大埔就正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n北區+大埔+沙田就負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望可以儘快取得共識 等文宣組做野"},{"pid":"57c71c670acb6b85147159e86344eb45209e7d39","tid":1653843,"uid":129828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"Tui 上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a477fc810c5526c8d3ace1498815b56fad465430","tid":1653843,"uid":129828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"44d056e3600c037a81dca41d79ef0f59d34b668c","tid":1653843,"uid":129828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:26:33.000Z","msg":"再tui"},{"pid":"9f67b64f282e5c28b751c3e044c313f3893fdbb2","tid":1653843,"uid":129828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:28:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90dcabd1f2800e4449259f2e1cf322bff61d0a3","tid":1653843,"uid":271739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"上次北區+大埔+沙田, 上水粉嶺大埔友好難走<br />\n如果北區+大埔 大埔集合既話 上水粉嶺人係咪都會好難走?"},{"pid":"31c72213f5db920309cc29c5aab69c3d